8b1bprog V0.01
8-Bit One-Bus Cartridge Programmer
Copyright 2010,2011,2012 The Free Software Foundation
Copyright 2011,2012 Everyday Inventors, LLC.

8-Bit One-Bus Cartridge Programmer is a hardware and firmware solution for
interfacing Flash memory cartridges to VT02 and above based computers and
game systems which have a dual-row 30-pin cartridge connector, for the
purpose of running home-brew and free software on VT02 and above based
systems.

The schematics are copyright Everyday Inventors, LLC. and licensed for use
under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike license as found at:

http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/

The firmware is copyright The Free Software Foundation, and Everyday
Inventors, LLC. and licensed for use under the GNU General Public License
version 3.0 (GPL V3.0) as found at:

http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

A plain-text copy of the GPL V3.0 is also provided in the firmware directory
of this project.
